:: StoryTitle
Hustle Journey


:: Welcome
What happens after graduation? Life isn't always as easy as landing a job right
after college. In The Hustle Journey, you step into the shoes of a fresh graduate
who must juggle multiple roles in order to survive. Experience the fun, challenges,
and tough decisions of being a jack-of-all-trades while navigating life after
university in search of success.

