:: I'm so tired!
After feeling tired of looking for the cell phone, I sat down on the edge of the bed.
It seemed pointless to continue searching now. It was midnight and now the sound of the
boarding house owner's owl was also sounding louder and louder, “hoo hoooo.” I lay down
slowly, staring at the ceiling of my room that was faintly illuminated by the lamplight.
Thoughts of tomorrow's event began to fade as my sleepiness overcame my soul.

Before I fell asleep, I wondered if they knew about my schedule tomorrow? tomorrow?



